<div style="font-size: 0.8em; font-weight: bold;">
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Before You Register on FundsForLife, Please be sure you are ready to pay. ie: Be ready to make transfer of the said amount to the matched user. or be ready to visit the bank should in case you can't make transfer. </span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Avoid SCAM!!. We have built this platform in a way to ensure scam is curbed. we will delete your account instantly if you are reported of scam.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Beggars Be warned!! you will be banned if you are reported.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Report anyone that asks for approval before making payment in the name of no money in his account.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Report anyone that refused to approve your payment after payment has been made. </span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Before sending any payment, make sure you call the person before sending payment. </span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">All amount to be donated must be available at hand.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Your donation must be made within 12 hours of been matched.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Any donor who does not upload proof of payment will be only responsible for account been blocked.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Any recipient who does not confirm payment received will be only responsible for account been blocked.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">Your account will be blocked if you upload fake proof of payment.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">To avoid delay in transaction and been blocked you are advised to activate your online money transfer with your bank.</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">After you make your donation you will be matched to received your own payment from other participants (incoming donation).</span></p><br><br>
<p><span class="text-danger" style="text-align: center; ">You do not need to Refer anybody, our system merge you automatically and you receive your payment. </span></p><br><br>
